title: sunny Como building
posting_body: ['We have two-bedroom apartments available for Fall 2022!', "This sunny Como building has a courtyard with large trees and picnic tables, workout area and communal storage in the basement, lots of kitchen storage, and it's in the perfect location!", 'Hang out at Van Cleve Park, with basketball and tennis courts, a playground, and a wading pool in the summer, or walk just around the corner to Black Coffee and Waffle Bar, or Football Pizza to grab a bite!', 'Just a few blocks south is vibrant', "Dinkytown, the University of Minnesota East Bank campus, TCF Stadium, and Stadium Village; a hungry student's heaven!", 'Nearby Como Ave, Hennepin Ave, University Ave, 35W, HWY 280, multiple major bus lines and the light rail, and lots of walking and biking paths mean that nothing you need is more than a few minutes away!']
